.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, thriller, scientific, romance, satire
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: mysterymaster, swimming, water-polo, rugby, biathlon
City: nizza, san-francisco, miami, edinburgh, rome
1. the british is the person watching scientific movies
2. the swedish is the person traveling to miami
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking coffee
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person traveling to san-francisco
7. the person watching satire movies is the person who's sport is swimming
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza
11. the person traveling to romes is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming
12. the person who's sport is mysterymaster is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the person who's sport is rugby
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies
15. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
